<p>Through all that research, LeadPages has discovered specific techniques that you can use to boost conversions and drive more sales.</p>
<p>During Thursday‚Äôs live training, LeadPages Conversion Educator Tim Paige will reveal four of these simple techniques.</p>
<p><a href="https://my.leadpages.net/wl/jspencer/">Register for Thursday‚Äôs all-new live training right now. </a>&lt;&#8211;</p>
<p>Inside Thursday‚Äôs live training, you‚Äôll also discover. . .</p>
